metadata.name: The Laugh of the Medusa
metadata.description:
Why is it called the laugh of Medusa?

"The Laugh of the Medusa" is successful in its creation of a writing style that allows women to claim authority because it was created on the foundation of the woman's claim to herself and her body, therefore eliminating the oppressive effects of patriarchal control of rhetoric.
...
The Laugh of the Medusa.
